modName: Lady of Death UNP and UNP Skinny
summary: Adaption of Lady of Death Set for CBBE V3 by newermind43 to fit the regular UNP body as well as the UNP Skinny body.
descriptionHtml:
Adaption of Newermind43s Lady of Death armour for UNP with weight sliders.
There is also a UNP Skinny version if anyone feel like using that one.

This is my first go at editing anything in 3DS Max, so if something looks way off, I'm sorry.
Send me a message and I'll see what I can do to fix it. Quite new to 3DS Max, so don't expect magic to happen.



Requirements and credits
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13761]Original Lady of Death for CBBE by Newermind43[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP Body by Dimon99 [/url]

Installed by overwriting the files.
